body.description: Why it is Necessary: -To prevent toddlers from frequently turning on the stove knob while adults are not paying attention; -To prevent babies from being injured by playing with the gas stove; -To protect toddlers from danger in the kitchen. Upgraded Version Double Lock System Our new upgraded dual-lock system further enhances kitchen safety. the stove knob comes is black color, making it easy for children to ignore them and difficult for them to figure out how to open them. However, they are designed to be very easy for adults to use with just one hand. These childproof oven knob covers are meant to prevent kids from accidentally turning on the stove or oven and getting injured. Baby Proof Stove Knob Covers: Gas stove knob locks for babyproofing effectively prevent children or pets from accidentally turning on the gas stove, keeping your hands free and ensuring family safety. Application Range Before purchasing our stove knob covers, please make sure your gas knobs meet the following size requirements: -The stoven clearance be 2-12mm./(0.08 inch-0.43 inch) -The stoven is slit. Not Supported Our stove safety knob covers do not work in the following cases: - Recessed knobs. - Knobs are too large. - The distance of the stove clearance is too short, less than 0.08 inches.
